  ShadowDensity: 1.000000
  Text: |-
    Scores: Stored in Supabase in the game_leaderboard_scores table, one best score per authenticated user. In this example, PinchGameController submits via GlobalLeaderboard when a round ends; the leaderboard refreshes with get_top_scores after each submission. Sorting is configurable (descending = higher wins, ascending = lower wins).
    
    Scaling:  Each authenticated player submits to the same shared leaderboard.
